{"id":44866,"title":"鋼之鍊金術師 2003年版","category":["奇幻","冒險"],"premiere":[2003,10,4],"ep":51,"author":"荒川弘","website":"","description":"背景設定在鍊金術相當發達的世界。愛德華·愛力克和他的弟弟阿爾馮斯十分思念亡故的母親，為了再次見到母親的微笑，而進行鍊金術中最大的禁忌「人體鍊成」──亦即讓死者復活的鍊成術──可是鍊成失敗時的反彈效應，愛德華付出「代價」左腳、阿爾則失去全身。為救回弟弟，愛德犧牲自己的右臂作為代價，將弟弟的靈魂固定在一副鎧甲上；而失去的右臂和左腿則由鋼製義肢「機械鎧」來替代，因此在取得國家鍊金術師資格時、大總統給予「鋼」的稱號，人們稱之為「鋼之鍊金術師」。鋼之鍊金術師用語列表公曆1911年，愛力克兄弟為取回他們所失去的一切，開始踏上了旅程。","image":"https://myself-bbs.com/data/attachment/forum/202401/18/132959rrgr3bmwnugnnunn.jpg","episodes":{"第 01 話":"AgADCA4AAjppQVU","第 02 話":"AgADCQ4AAjppQVU","第 03 話":"AgADCw4AAjppQVU","第 04 話":"AgADDQ4AAjppQVU","第 05 話":"AgADDg4AAjppQVU","第 06 話":"AgADDw4AAjppQVU","第 07 話":"AgADFg4AAjppQVU","第 08 話":"AgADFw4AAjppQVU","第 09 話":"AgADHQ4AAjppQVU","第 10 話":"AgADJA4AAjppQVU","第 11 話":"AgADQA4AAjppQVU","第 12 話":"AgADQg4AAjppQVU","第 13 話":"AgADyQ4AAjppQVU","第 14 話":"AgADzg4AAjppQVU","第 15 話":"AgAD1A4AAjppQVU","第 16 話":"AgAD2g4AAjppQVU","第 17 話":"AgAD3A4AAjppQVU","第 18 話":"AgAD3w4AAjppQVU","第 19 話":"AgAD4A4AAjppQVU","第 20 話":"AgAD4g4AAjppQVU","第 21 話":"AgAD5A4AAjppQVU","第 22 話":"AgAD5Q4AAjppQVU","第 23 話":"AgAD5g4AAjppQVU","第 24 話":"AgAD5w4AAjppQVU","第 25 話":"AgADDA8AAjppQVU","第 26 話":"AgADDQ8AAjppQVU","第 27 話":"AgADDg8AAjppQVU","第 28 話":"AgADDw8AAjppQVU","第 29 話":"AgADEA8AAjppQVU","第 30 話":"AgADEQ8AAjppQVU","第 31 話":"AgADFQ8AAjppQVU","第 32 話":"AgADGA8AAjppQVU","第 33 話":"AgADHg8AAjppQVU","第 34 話":"AgADKQ8AAjppQVU","第 35 話":"AgADNQ8AAjppQVU","第 36 話":"AgADPA8AAjppQVU","第 37 話":"AgADPg8AAjppQVU","第 38 話":"AgADUg8AAjppQVU","第 39 話":"AgADUw8AAjppQVU","第 40 話":"AgADVA8AAjppQVU","第 41 話":"AgADVQ8AAjppQVU","第 42 話":"AgADVg8AAjppQVU","第 43 話":"AgADVw8AAjppQVU","第 44 話":"AgAD7AsAAjppSVU","第 45 話":"AgAD7QsAAjppSVU","第 46 話":"AgAD7gsAAjppSVU","第 47 話":"AgAD7wsAAjppSVU","第 48 話":"AgAD8QsAAjppSVU","第 49 話":"AgAD8gsAAjppSVU","第 50 話":"AgAD9AsAAjppSVU","第 51 話":"AgAD9QsAAjppSVU","劇場版 香巴拉的征服者":"AgADOhMAAuvJuVU"}}